description: Erection of part 3-, part 4-, part 5-, part 9- and part 11-storey building to provide 48 affordable flats (19 one-bedroom, 22 two-bedroom and 7 three-bedroom) and 79 private flats (25 one-bedroom and 54 two-bedroom), 2 floors of basement/semi-basement parking with 104 car spaces including 4 disabled spaces and 30 bicycle parking spaces on the lower floor and 54 car parking space including 4 disabled spaces, 52 bicycle parking spaces and 5 motorcycle spaces on the upper floor and 166 square metres of community or commercial space within Use Classes A1, A2, B1 and D2 on ground floor fronting Park Lane, provision of landscaping including children's play area and waste storage and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 19th August 2005 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended and as accompanied by:
